                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "To solve the equation\n\n\\[\n\\sin(x) + x^2 = 42\n\\]\n\nI'll find the value(s) of \\( x \\) that satisfy this equation. Since this is a transcendental equation (it contains both a trigonometric and polynomial term), we'll solve it numerically.\n\nLet's proceed to find the solution(s).",
